# project-overview

## What this repo is

`fastapi-app` is a single package repository written primarily in Python. Detected frameworks/tools: FastAPI, Pydantic, SQLAlchemy, Alembic, pytest.

## Languages

- Python (7 files)

## Frameworks

- FastAPI — web
- Pydantic — validation
- SQLAlchemy — orm
- Alembic — migrations
- pytest — test
- Ruff — lint
- mypy — typecheck

## Package managers

- pip (`pyproject.toml`)

## Layout

- `alembic/` — database migrations
- `app/` — application
- `tests/` — tests
